<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="large-adj">large <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /lɑːdʒ/    美 /lɑːrdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(体积、容积、面积等方面) 大的；巨大的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a large garden / house 
大花园/房子</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>多的；量大的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a large population 
人口众多</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-large">at large</h3>
<p>1.<strong>整个；全部；未被捕获的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The chemical pollution has a great effect on the world at large.
化学污染对整个世界有很大的影响。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>largely /'lɑːdʒli/ adv   </p></div>